         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Year 22, Pharmouthi 8. Give from the account of Julius Theon and Julius theon to Horos of the [   ], employed in the bath-house of the town house, for his wages from the 5th to the 8th inclusive, 4 days, 4 drachmas. (2nd hd.) Give the 4 drachmas."</ab>
